<Layout title="RdN: Sobre Nosotros">
    <main class="bg-gray-50 overflow-x-hidden">
        
        <section class="relative pt-20 pb-48 lg:pb-64 bg-[url(/nosotros/bannerNosotros.webp)] bg-cover bg-blue-950 bg-blend-soft-light isolate">
            
            <div class="absolute top-0 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 w-[800px] h-[500px] bg-blue-600/20 rounded-full blur-[120px] -z-10"></div>

            <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 text-center relative z-10">
                
                <span class="text-blue-200 font-bold tracking-[0.2em] text-sm md:text-base uppercase animate-fade-in-down font-sans">
					Sobre Nosotros
				</span>
                
                <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl lg:text-8xl font-PlayfairDisplay font-bold text-white mb-8 leading-tight animate-fade-in-up">
                    Ciencia con <br />
                    <span class="relative inline-block">
                        <span class="absolute bottom-2 left-0 w-full h-4 bg-blue-600/30 -rotate-1 -z-10 rounded-sm"></span>
                        Propósito Humano
                    </span>
                </h1>
                
                <p class="text-xl text-gray-200 leading-relaxed font-sans max-w-2xl mx-auto animate-fade-in-up animate-delay-100">
                    Somos un ecosistema interdisciplinario donde la excelencia académica y la ética profesional convergen.
                </p>

            </div>
        </section>

        <div class="relative z-20 px-6 -mt-32 lg:-mt-48 mb-24 animate-expand-vertically">
            <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto relative">
                
                <div class="rounded-3xl overflow-hidden shadow-2xl shadow-blue-950 border-3 border-white">
                    <img 
                        src="/nosotros/team.webp" 
                        alt="Equipo RdN" 
                        class="w-full aspect-video lg:aspect-21/9 object-cover"
                        loading="lazy"
                    />
                </div>

                <div class="absolute -bottom-10 -right-4 md:right-10 bg-blue-950 p-6 md:p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-xl max-w-xs border border-white/10 animate-fade-in-left delay-300 hidden sm:block">
                    <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-3">
                        <div class="p-3 bg-blue-50 text-blue-950 rounded-full">
                            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2" stroke="currentColor" class="w-6 h-6">
                                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M15 19.128a9.38 9.38 0 0 0 2.625.372 9.337 9.337 0 0 0 4.121-.952 4.125 4.125 0 0 0-7.533-2.493M15 19.128v-.003c0-1.113-.285-2.16-.786-3.07M15 19.128v.106A12.318 12.318 0 0 1 8.624 21c-2.331 0-4.512-.645-6.374-1.766l-.001-.109a6.375 6.375 0 0 1 11.964-3.07M12 6.375a3.375 3.375 0 1 1-6.75 0 3.375 3.375 0 0 1 6.75 0Zm8.25 2.25a2.625 2.625 0 1 1-5.25 0 2.625 2.625 0 0 1 5.25 0Z" />
                            </svg>
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <p class="text-3xl font-bold text-white">+50</p>
                            <p class="text-xs text-blue-200 font-bold uppercase tracking-wider">Miembros Activos</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <p class="text-sm text-blue-100 mt-2 border-t border-white/20 pt-2 text-pretty">
                        Un equipo interdisciplinario unido por la ciencia y la salud.
                    </p>
                </div>

            </div>
        </div>

        <section class="pt-24 pb-52 px-6 relative z-20">
            <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto">
                
                <div class="relative rounded-[3rem] shadow-2xl bg-white overflow-hidden min-h-[500px] flex flex-col md:block">
                    
                    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-blue-950 w-full md:w-[55%] h-1/2 md:h-full z-0 md:-skew-x-12 md:-ml-20 origin-left"></div>
                    
                    <div class="relative z-10 grid md:grid-cols-2 h-full">
                        
                        <div class="p-12 lg:p-16 flex flex-col justify-center h-full">
                            <div class="inline-flex p-3 bg-white/10 border border-white/20 rounded-xl text-white mb-6 w-fit">
                                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2" stroke="currentColor" class="w-8 h-8"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M3 3v1.5M3 21v-6m0 0 2.77-.693a9 9 0 0 1 6.208.682l.108.054a9 9 0 0 0 6.086.71l3.114-.732a48.524 48.524 0 0 1-.005-10.499l-3.11.732a9 9 0 0 1-6.085-.711l-.108-.054a9 9 0 0 0-6.208-.682L3 4.5M3 15V4.5" /></svg>
                            </div>
                            <h2 class="text-4xl font-PlayfairDisplay font-bold text-white mb-6">Nuestra Misión</h2>
                            <p class="text-blue-100/90 leading-relaxed text-lg font-light md:max-w-md">
                                Contribuir de forma interdisciplinaria en la formación académica, investigación y buenas prácticas clínicas, con altos estándares de ética.
                            </p>
                        </div>

                        <div class="p-12 lg:p-16 flex flex-col justify-center h-full md:pl-20">
                            <div class="inline-flex p-3 bg-blue-50 border border-blue-100 rounded-xl text-blue-950 mb-6 w-fit">
